name: Warm Parasitic Grub
text: If you control no monsters you can Special Summon this card from your hand. You can only Special Summon 1 "Warm Parasitic Grub" per turn this way. This card can attack directly. If this card deals damage to your opponent’s LP: send the top 3 cards of your opponent’s deck to the GY. If this card is destroyed: send the top 2 cards of your opponent's Deck to the GY.
